The grizzled old man sitting by the fire within the confines of the Smokey Potato Inn.  He asks you to journey forth and find him a goblin skull his daughter lost in a cave to the East.
You find a young terrified woman who is running towards you on the open path.  She franticly requests your assistance with dispatching some vile creatures in a clearing to the East.
The portly mayor of the small town has asked you to eliminate the monsters in a cave nearby.
An elderly widow has asked you to kill the group of monsters in the forest who killed her son last week.
The crippled officer has asked for your help in avenging him against the vile creatures that injured him and stole his pet chicken.
